data.description: Finally, an affordable home located in the popular neighborhood of Sylvan Shores where your neighbors are friendly and still ride bikes and take leisurely walks.  This home is on a corner location with a driving access to the newly installed out building that the Seller is leaving on the property.  This 12' x 26' outbuilding has many outlets, a mini split and full insultation with vinyl flooring.   Could you use this as a hobby room? a workshop? a home office?   The Seller has placed slider screens across the front carport to enhance the front porch; however, if you prefer to park your car, the sliders are easy to remove.  The large second bathroom has a modern, newly purchased washer/dryer (all in one) combination which Seller states is energy efficient.  There are two additional storage units in the back yard.   Come see the charm of this 1960 built home. **New roof shingles**  Schedule a showing today!
